<Layout 
  title="Products - Trenddit Client | AI-First Enterprise Intelligence Platform"
  description="Discover Trenddit Client - the flagship AI-first intelligence platform for enterprise technology decisions, featuring multi-agent analysis, predictive forecasting, and strategic recommendations. Plus Trenddit Memo Chrome extension for knowledge management."
